{{Wikibooks|R Programming}}
This book aims to introduce the principles of statistics and modern statistical analysis for a non-mathematical audience, using the free statistical package [[R Programming|R]].

If you are just browsing, we recommend setting up your [[Special:Mypage/monobook.css|personal Wikibooks style]] as specified in [[/Statistics and R#Setting up wikibooks]].

