== What is Finance? == Finance is a branch of economics, a science that studies the management of funds (money and other assets). More specifically, through financial analysis, decisions and corrective actions can be taken regarding the collection and use those funds as to optimize their use toward the objectives of an organization (states, companies and businesses) or individual.
Types of finance: # Overdraft # Bank term loans # Asset-based finance # Receivables Finance # Invoice discounting # Angel funding # Venture capital # Personal resources
